Introduction

Visionary Vision, also shortened to VV and stylized Vision@ry Vision, is the ninth sub-unit of the girl group tripleS under MODHAUS. The unit consisted of twelve members selected by both the fans and the agency.

YuBin and Lynn were selected as the two first members on June 13, 2024. HyeRin was chosen as the leader of the unit on June 15. Kaede, Kotone, YeonJi, and SoHyun were revealed as members on June 16. The same day, NaKyoung was announced to be the leader pick, meaning that HyeRin had chosen her to be part of the unit. On June 18, YooYeon, Nien, Xinyu, and JiYeon were revealed as the four last members of the unit.

Vision@ry Vision made their debut on October 23, 2024 with the full-length album "Performante".

On November 5, 2024, they recieved their first music show win for "Hit The Floor". This achievement makes them the first tripleS unit to get a music show win.
